{"id":"19bc2de5-f698-428f-a64e-7f0c8e219e73","name":"Knox Kaine","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/ehi1WZLqZSOSse6XG3aT8.webp\" style=\"width: 725px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"><br>ALT | <span style=\"color: rgb(18, 204, 87);\">Villain-Verse </span>| Knox has his sights set on one thing this Christmas season. The expensive ornament that will be raffled off during the high-society Christmas gala in Parkham City this year. Dressing in something other then his signature villain outfit for once to blend in, Knox was lucky this year's theme was to honor the heroes of the city and required masks for attendees. Sneaking off through a side hallway, however, ends in a meeting he wasn't expecting. Literally bumping into the hero guest of honor at the event, you.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>But wait, was that... Mistletoe above the doorway?</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">┈┈┈┈․° ☣ °․┈┈┈┈<br></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">🔊 <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://soundcloud.com/nallak-bot-audios/mistletoe-mishap-narrated-knox-kaine-intro?si=6289c3f9c72d46c38b54830acd8257e7&amp;utm_source=clipboard&amp;utm_medium=text&amp;utm_campaign=social_sharing\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(16, 194, 22);\"><strong>[Narrated Intro]</strong></span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>^ Listen to the first message narrated by Knox Kaine with sound effects on SoundCloud</strong>!</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">┈┈┈┈․° ☣ °․┈┈┈┈</p><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Knox Alternates!</em></h3><p style=\"text-align: center;\">~ <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/2d73fb11-7674-4bad-90bb-e6b411abe263_character-knox-kaine\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(37, 176, 46);\">[You're injured and appear at Knox's door for help]</span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">~ <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"